{"tid":2114973,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[Linux] 你地用開咩去backup 啲file?","createTime":"2020-07-19T08:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T04:45:01.000Z","uid":18641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0fefb1f56b4b87819c54b5c3b52d0be7ee373c91","tid":2114973,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:04:53.000Z","msg":"我而家有部機係pop os, ext4. 諗住將所有files 放晒係呢部linux 機再開files sharing 等我另一部主機同啲laptop 都睇到同改到啲files, 然後定期backup 部pop os 啲files.<br />\n<br />\n我見rsync, deja dup, timeshift 呢幾隻都多人講，你地覺得邊隻backup好用？"},{"pid":"e4df0cfe8741a806f3f859cee70a2b44976c5938","tid":2114973,"uid":281306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:47:32.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0931944f77d734ae9c20628bb494c0a823afb09","tid":2114973,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"timeshift 操作 都簡單"},{"pid":"dbae6324880752b8277749969dd4e00d6374a5e2","tid":2114973,"uid":355997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T14:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> block level : rsync, dd, 快好多, 可以成隻disk clone"},{"pid":"5d6bccacb55ddab1f619e7e7a5dfab4e35705033","tid":2114973,"uid":123988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbae6324880752b8277749969dd4e00d6374a5e2","tid":2114973,"uid":355997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T14:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> block level : rsync, dd, 快好多, 可以成隻disk clone"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"係dd 好快，但係之後要restore又麻煩少少<br />\n<br />\n我覺得用得linux,緊係cron job,<br />\n<br />\ndaily tar 左個share folder, <br />\n<br />\n再ftp upload 上backup drive<br />\n或者cp 去usb ext harddisk<br />\n<br />\n仲可以keep一個月或者兩個月<br />\n每日比多個email 話你